data.description: Looking for a mountain retreat from the everyday hustle and bustle here it is! This lovely home has been remodeled and updated and has a brand new roof. Enjoy countless hours on your porch watching the elk and wildlife while having your morning coffee or tea in the afternoon. Prepare your meals with veggies fresh from your garden, then shower off in the mud room. You will have plenty of room for all your pets, chickens, horses,& toys on this 1.03 acre fenced lot. There is even a fully functional meat shop! You can use to process your own game & livestock. Plus your own private well. Plenty of room for your R.V . National forest close by! Pear tree is  producing pears. This is a homesteaders' paradise! Grow & raise your own food! Meat shop is 10x15, plus 10x15 storage room ,& 30x20 garage.
